item.title: Which Is Better?
item.dc:creator: @dave5534 dave5534
item.description:
@dave5534 wrote:

Well if you read Sumillions it sounds better
Sumillions

- Flawless walking. - Multiple users can be used ! - Smooth mining, if someone else mined it away, it will move on. - Mines Mith as well, once it sees it, it wont stop mining it until its gone Big Grin - AntiBan (at choice) - AntiRandoms from SRL, guaranteed to be good. - Nice progress reporter - AutoColored!! For all you lazy peeps out there, no need to fill it in ! - Easy to use forms, if you still don't understand them ill be more than happy to explain. - Very own openbank procedures, never failed me and i've tried to make it fail Wink - Improved Anti-gas!! (had complaints about it :S) - Attaches Paxe-head when it flies off ! (not 100%) - In the slight chance that the paxe will be lost, it will get the best paxe there is from the bank
Mad cow's
-PERFECT auto-colour -New walking procedure that is more efficient and faster -Use with unlimited accounts -Superior mining procedure -Forms to make it simple -News system -And it's currently OPEN SOURCE
Also Mad Cow's is 250k more.
